OL,3,CTwo men die after entering sea to help
OL,4,Cchildren in difficulty
OL,6,FTwo men have died after going into the
OL,7,Fsea to try to help two children who
OL,8,Fhad got into difficulty, Cleveland
OL,9,FPolice said.
OL,11,FThe force said that officers were
OL,12,Fcalled at around 3.45pm after concerns
OL,13,Fwere raised for two children who had
OL,14,Fgot into difficulty in the water at
OL,15,FSeaton Carew beach in Hartlepool.
OL,17,FTwo men entered the sea to assist the
OL,18,Fchildren, who were taken to hospital
OL,19,Fto be checked over and are now
OL,20,Fconfirmed to be safe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
