PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1783973917
OL,3,CTwo men die after entering sea to help
OL,4,Cchildren in difficulty
OL,6,FRNLI staff brought the men out of the
OL,7,Fwater and they received immediate
OL,8,Fmedical treatment, the police said.
OL,10,FBut both men were pronounced dead a
OL,11,Fshort time later.
OL,13,FSuperintendent Glen Ward said: "Our
OL,14,Fdeepest sympathies go out to the
OL,15,Ffamilies of both the men involved in
OL,16,Fthis tragic incident today.
OL,18,F"Despite the best efforts of emergency
OL,19,Fservices, sadly both men were
OL,20,Fpronounced dead a short time after
OL,21,Fbeing brought out of the sea.
OL,26,@uD@`OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
