OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1783973917
OL,3,CTwo men die after entering sea to help
OL,4,Cchildren in difficulty
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"We are conducting enquiries into the
OL,12,Fcircumstances of what happened today,
OL,13,Falthough the deaths are not being
OL,14,Ftreated as suspicious and a file will
OL,15,Fbe prepared for the coroner.
OL,17,F"I would like to remind everyone that
OL,18,Fopen water comes with serious risks.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
