PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1783973917
OL,3,CTwo men die after entering sea to help
OL,4,Cchildren in difficulty
OL,6,F"We know it is inviting in the hot
OL,7,Fweather, but we would encourage people
OL,8,Fto refrain from entering any open
OL,9,Fwater at all. Today we have sadly seen
OL,10,Fthe true tragedy that can happen as a
OL,11,Fresult.
OL,13,F"Please take extra care and enjoy the
OL,14,Fwarm weather as safely as possible."
OL,16,FThe force said that specially trained
OL,17,Fofficers were supporting both families.
OL,19,FIt follows a number of water-related
OL,20,Fdeaths in recent days amid the hot
OL,21,Fweather.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@dO]
